wikipedia_page.main: Henry Mortlock Aitken (8 January 1831 – 12 August 1915) was an English cricketer active in the 1850s.

response: Aitken died at Hove at the age of 78. His brother Henry Aitken also played cricket for Oxford.
Henry Aitken is the name of several prominent people:
*Henry Aitken (mayor) (1840–99, mayor of Oamaru, New Zealand
